== Welcome == '''Welcome!''' (''We can't say that loudly enough!'')'''

Hello, 94.0.148.130, and '''''[[Wikipedia:Welcoming committee/Welcome to Wikipedia|welcome to Wikipedia]]!''''' I hope you like the place and decide to stay. Here are some pages you might find helpful:

* [[Wikipedia:Be bold in updating pages|'''Be Bold!''']] * [[Wikipedia:Avoiding common mistakes|Learn from others]] * [[Wikipedia:Etiquette|Be kind to others]] * [[Wikipedia:Contributing to Wikipedia|Contribute, Contribute, Contribute!]] * [[Wikipedia:User page|Tell us a bit about yourself]] * [[Help:Wikipedia: The Missing Manual|Our great guide to Wikipedia]] If you have any questions or problems, no matter what they are, leave me a message on my talk page. Or, please come to the '''[[Wikipedia:New contributors' help page|new contributors' help page]]''', where experienced Wikipedians can answer any queries you have! Or, you can just type '''{{helpme}}''' on your user page, and someone will show up shortly to answer your questions. Please sign your name on talk pages and votes by typing ~~~~; our software automatically converts it to your username and the date. We're so glad you're here!
